{"tid":1002942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環新世界大廈男童墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-01-31T09:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T05:57:40.000Z","uid":41404,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"397c9fbf8e36f5741384e72939637cc46cdad930","tid":1002942,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"中環皇后大道中16號至18號新世界大廈，今日（31日）下午2時許，一名男童由上址高處墮下，重創倒臥大廈平台。消防及救護員接報趕至，先將男童帶返地面，再由救護車送院搶救，惜最後傷重不治，警方正調查男童墮樓原因。 <br />\n<br />\n東方報業集團(下稱「東方」)記者採訪期間，男童的兩名外籍男女親友，突然情緒激動，一手搶去記者的攝錄機掟落地上，又起飛腳踢落記者的相機袋，令袋內一支鏡頭損毀，東方記者已就事件報警處理。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/mobile/bkn-20190131155643325-0131_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190131%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190131155643325-0131_00822_001.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6hdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=e10faf02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190131/mobile/bkn-20190131155643325-0131_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a2d36e7a8ff80ac97ab4ed2939f8a166a1a9c941","tid":1002942,"uid":3028,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"parkour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac02f79aee464c6e186c01c6b21ce1f389b201fa","tid":1002942,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a76bf36e74b3631f6e72857b68f56f868ca59a","tid":1002942,"uid":48759,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"支那人：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywZFk6O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywZFk6O.png&h=c7bd7d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新移民：<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/bL3bsMW.png[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbL3bsMW.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d